    <item>
      <title>非法直播体育赛事已成主流。我们能做些什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/how-illegal-streaming-of-live-sport-went-mainstream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[广播公司正面临着全球范围内非法直播体育赛事现象的激增，这使他们损失了数百亿美元的潜在收入，而他们似乎对此无能为力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/how-illegal-streaming-of-live-sport-went-mainstream</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 14:21:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
